  "code": "%%{Groupware_WikiPage}}}%%\n\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant User\n    participant Vault as YieldVaultMultiAsset<br/>(Groupware_KanbanBoard)\n    participant Aave as Aave V3 Pool<br/>(Groupware_ChatRoom)\n    participant RSC as YieldOptimizerRsc<br/>(Groupware_ChatRoom)\n    participant Callback as Callback Proxy<br/>(Groupware_ChatRoom)\n\n    Note over User,Callback: Yield Monitoring and Rebalancing Flow\n\n    User->>Vault: triggerYieldSnapshot(Groupware_IssueTracker)\n    Vault->>Aave: getReserveData(Groupware_ChatRoom)\n    Aave-->>Vault: liquidityRate, APY data\n    Vault->>Vault: Calculate APYs for all assets\n    Vault-->>RSC: emit YieldSnapshot(Groupware_ChatRoom)\n    \n    Note over RSC: RSC analyzes yield data\n    RSC->>RSC: Compare APYs across assets\n    RSC->>RSC: Determine optimal allocation\n    \n    alt Yield difference exceeds threshold\n        RSC->>Callback: emit Callback(Groupware_ChatRoom)\n        Callback->>Vault: executeRebalance(Groupware_KanbanBoard)\n        Vault->>Vault: Update asset allocations\n        Vault-->>User: Funds rebalanced to higher yield\n    else Yield difference below threshold\n        Note over RSC: No rebalance needed\n    end\n",
